high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the white table, and then turn right towards the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Look up to see the apple on the counter.
Slice the apple in three with the knife..
Take a step to the right towards the small black table.
Place the knife to the left of the salt shakers on the table.
Take a step to the right.
Pick up a slice of the apple.
Turn right and head towards the sink on your left.
Place the apple slice in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Turn around, take a step forward, turn right towards the white table, turn right towards the small black table.
Place the slice of apple to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of apple along with a knife on the small black table.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk over to the counter on the left-hand side of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Walk forward and closer to the counter.
Cut a slice from the apple on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the table beside the oven.
Turn right and place the knife bedside the salt and pepper shakers on the black table beside the counter that the apple is on.
Turn right and move to the counter beside the sink.
Pick up the slice of apple from the counter.
Turn right and move to the sink basin.
Wash the apple slice in the sink.
Turn right and walk back to the black table the the knife was placed on.
Place the apple slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Placing a clean apple slice on a table.

high_descs: Move to the white counter on the left side of the sink.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Find the green apple that is also on the counter.
Slice the green apple  on the counter.
Take the knife and move to the small black table by the white counter where you are working.
Put the knife on the small black table.
Move to the right back to the counter with the sliced apple.
Pick up the apple that is on the counter.
Move to the right to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink and turn on the water.
Wash the apple and turn off the water. Pick up the apple.
Move to the right to the small black table with the knife.  Put the apple on the table.
